{"tid":2247689,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[學佛][阿彌陀佛] 拼命念佛，名召萬德","createTime":"2020-10-18T05:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T08:25:42.000Z","uid":347001,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c68b8b13b36917d64c40a8a54e9cb27726e12c8e","tid":2247689,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"【淨空老法師】<br />\n<br />\n我們每個學佛的同學都懂得一句話，實際上是似懂非懂。積功累德，都知道我要積功累德，怎麼積法？不知道。每天做好事、行善、素食、放生，幹這些，不知道那個是有德，很少。不如念佛。<br />\n<br />\n念佛名號萬德，你那些小德統統在裡頭，沒人知道。<br />\n真正知道的人，這個人會拼命念佛，名召萬德，這才是真正積功累德，不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n2014 淨土大經科註  第 226 集"},{"pid":"4c9cb07f69a33d4c690b1f21589485e53357f720","tid":2247689,"uid":347001,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68b8b13b36917d64c40a8a54e9cb27726e12c8e","tid":2247689,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"【淨空老法師】<br />\n<br />\n我們每個學佛的同學都懂得一句話，實際上是似懂非懂。積功累德，都知道我要積功累德，怎麼積法？不知道。每天做好事、行善、素食、放生，幹這些，不知道那個是有德，很少。不如念佛。<br />\n<br />\n念佛名號萬德，你那些小德統統在裡頭，沒人知道。<br />\n真正知道的人，這個人會拼命念佛，名召萬德，這才是真正積功累德，不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n2014 淨土大經科註  第 226 集"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;分隔線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n念念不忘阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用起底功能 翻看其他智慧經文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"pink\">佛教是教育，不是宗教，教什麼？教我們修清淨心，教我們幸福快樂，教我們健康長壽，過幸福美滿的人生<br />\n<br />\n同時教我們宇宙真相💫<br />\n<br />\n學佛是人生最高的享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿彌陀佛🙏🏻</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">學佛就是將佛陀的教誨落實到日常生活當中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小妹的學佛筆記🙏🏻還在努力學習當中🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdvWbzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdvWbzO.png&h=b69b0f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF0mSOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF0mSOt.png&h=ca310694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMATQwD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMATQwD.png&h=4d6eba3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與佛有緣的同修可以在Facebook search 淨空法師/阿彌陀佛/念佛成佛 搜索更多經文+智慧字句<br />\n許多佛菩薩都把經文的精華/重點節錄了出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Famituofobuddha%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=882860c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FnianAmitabha%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=38efc63f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkanpofanxia%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=dc5f9572\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"large\">或在ig 搜索 amitabha_hk</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\">佛說現在是末法時期 淨宗法門成就<br />\n淨宗法門念的是一句「阿彌陀佛」<br />\n看的是一部《無量壽經》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文字版看上此網站瀏覽完整版無量壽經<br />\n<a href=\"http://ft.hwadzan.tw/index_as.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fft.hwadzan.tw%2Findex_as.php&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=7af1b552\" target=\"_blank\">http://ft.hwadzan.tw/index_as.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPQ9